com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.typedec
Interface NativeStaticFieldMethodSignature

All Superinterfaces:
NativeBehaviorSignature, NativeFieldMethodSignature
public interface NativeStaticFieldMethodSignature
extends NativeFieldMethodSignature

The NativeStaticFieldMethodSignature interface represents the native signature declaration of static native field-methods.

Author:
Jose M. Arranz Santamaria
See Also:
NativeSignatureManager.decStaticFieldMethod(Object,int)

Method Detail

getField

java.lang.reflect.Field getField(java.lang.Class containerClass,
                                 java.lang.String fieldName)
Returns the field reflection object with the specified field name and container class.

If there is no Java field with this name and class or field type is different an exception is thrown.

Parameters:
containerClass - the container class of the field.
fieldName - the field name to find.
Returns:
the java.lang.reflect.Field object found.

decStaticFieldMethod

TypeNativeStaticFieldMethod decStaticFieldMethod(java.lang.Class fieldClass)
Declares a native static field-method type using the specified native field class and this signature.

Current implementation is:

return getTypeManager().decStaticFieldMethod(fieldClass,this);

Parameters:
fieldClass - the native field class or interface to use.
Returns:
the native type of the declaration.
See Also:
NativeTypeManager.decStaticFieldMethod(Class,NativeStaticFieldMethodSignature), NativeBehaviorSignature.decBehavior(Class)

newStaticFieldMethodReflection

NativeStaticFieldMethodReflection newStaticFieldMethodReflection(java.lang.Class containerClass,
                                                                 java.lang.String fieldName)
Creates a native static field reflection wrapper using this signature and the specified container class and field name.

It is implemented calling NativeBehaviorSignature.newBehaviorReflection(Member) with the field returned by getField(Class,String) using the specified class and field name.

Parameters:
containerClass - the container class of the field.
fieldName - the field name to find.
Returns:
a new NativeStaticFieldMethodReflection object as a callback of the specified field.

newDirectStaticFieldCallback

NativeDirectStaticFieldCallback newDirectStaticFieldCallback(java.lang.Class containerClass,
                                                             java.lang.String fieldName)
Creates a new direct static field callback of the Java field using this signature and the specified container class and field name.

It is implemented calling NativeBehaviorSignature.newDirectCallback(Member) with the field returned by getField(Class,String) using the specified class and field name.

Parameters:
containerClass - the container class of the field.
fieldName - the field name to find.
Returns:
a new NativeDirectStaticFieldCallback as a callback of the specified field.
